{"tid":1949432,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有種心態，想同各位手足分享一種心態 — LESS EGO","createTime":"2020-03-29T15:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T13:31:44.000Z","uid":82955,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4ccd28b868270f14e59f7cd44abb5f010b2649b4","tid":1949432,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">首先賣個廣告，<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>HKPOSTMANCHANNEL</strong></span>係一個郵寄文宣嘅行動平台，主打低成本脫離同溫層做文宣。我地都掙扎緊嘗試緊做一啲心靈支援同堆齊上齊學嘅內容。希望有興趣嘅你follow我地ig/ tg &mdash; <a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkpostmanchannel?igshid=p06v8ydbogfs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkpostmanchannel%3Figshid%3Dp06v8ydbogfs&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=ebcf3ae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkpostmanchannel?igshid=p06v8ydbogfs</a> / <a href=\"https://t.me/hkpostmanchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpostmanchannel&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=c1ddd376\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpostmanchannel</a></span><br />\n<br />\n係呢到，想冒昧同各位手足分享一種心態。<br />\n因為要光復香港，我地必需要先光復自己。<br />\n同行手足，我地一齊為呢個民族嘅思想同心態好好GEAR UP。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論，齊上齊學<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eS3f2y1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeS3f2y1.png&h=36aacada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTSXwsm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTSXwsm.png&h=47a63d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Up5NTFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUp5NTFJ.png&h=9ce194d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzswAT4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzswAT4.png&h=540f58ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9hD0kL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9hD0kL.png&h=23f61691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kxqVh7s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkxqVh7s.png&h=8e6a02fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSD0kO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSD0kO.png&h=311ce401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfufh7u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgfufh7u.png&h=077d4058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n永遠愛你地呀手足，好好繼續光復自己，好好同行。<br />\n順帶一提，咁靚嘅畫係由手足所畫，歡迎follow，會有驚喜 &mdash; <a href=\"https://instagram.com/arkisan.hk?igshid=1xjyx54lrvc3f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Farkisan.hk%3Figshid%3D1xjyx54lrvc3f&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=b788e3bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/arkisan.hk?igshid=1xjyx54lrvc3f</a>"},{"pid":"6fd35b590af8999022faeb4240a004298ae2ce0e","tid":1949432,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"希望認同嘅你會幫推同follow我地，有諗法嘅你會留言，齊上齊學。掙扎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd26ba6631aa0be2badbe992970ae7eb6d3551ce","tid":1949432,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55ad4d6e111736df07334fa7f476d18175942c63","tid":1949432,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"我地會掙扎跟新嘅任務同嘗試打國際線，人手真係唔夠，推Post就輕輕交比大家了，希望大家可以大力推幾下🙏🏻"},{"pid":"0ec5ec506cf5bac7eb977f66bec4ef217ddbb72c","tid":1949432,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29